Tech Stack
Frontend (Game Rendering & UI)
HTML5 & CSS3 – For structure and styling.
TypeScript – Core scripting language for interactivity.
Canvas API (2D) – For rendering graphics.
Phaser.js – A great game engine for 2D browser games with physics, animations, and scene management.

Backend (Multiplayer, Game State, and Logic)
Node.js – High-performance server-side runtime.
Express.js – Web framework for API and game state management.
Socket.IO – Real-time communication for multiplayer features.
PostgreSQL – Database for storing user progress and game data.
